            <title>[LU-16858] Remove some obsolete configure options</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16858</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have some very old configure options that are never set and should never be set, because they now represent untested code paths and/or features that can be disabled in other ways (or can no longer be disabled - ie Lustre can&apos;t work without them). &#160;This ticket is a catch-all for a removing a few of these.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
